<name>ENGINE</name>
<section id="10006_S0004" variety="S0004">
<name>2AZ-FE ENGINE CONTROL SYSTEM</name>
<ttl id="10006_S0004_731VM_T00FT" variety="T00FT">
<name>ENGINE COOLANT TEMPERATURE SENSOR</name>
<para id="RM0000012NJ004X" category="G" type-id="3001K" name-id="ES10A-05" from="200601">
<name>INSPECTION</name>
<subpara id="RM0000012NJ004X_01" type-id="01" category="01">
<s-1 id="RM0000012NJ004X_01_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___0000B4Q00000">
<ptxt>INSPECT ENGINE COOLANT TEMPERATURE SENSOR</ptxt>
<content1 releasenbr="1">
<s2>
<ptxt>Using an ohmmeter, measure the resistance between the terminals.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="A114776E01" width="2.775699831in" height="4.7836529in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="2">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="2.07in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.06in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>20°C (68°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>2.32 to 2.59 kΩ</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>80°C (176°F)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>0.310 to 0.326 kΩ</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
<ptxt>If the result is not as specified, replace the sensor.</ptxt>
<atten3>
<ptxt>In case of checking the water temperature sensor in the water, do not allow water to go into the terminals. After checking, dry the sensor.</ptxt>
</atten3>
</s2>
</content1>
</s-1>
</subpara>
</para>
</ttl>
</section>
</servcat>
</pub>
</tmc-service-inc>